# Job Portal Module — Implementation Plan

Student job portal with admin-controlled postings, automatic eligibility engine, application & referral flows.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **CGPA & Backlog**: The system has **no CGPA field** and **no backlog tracking**. Two options:
> - **Option A (Recommended)**: Skip CGPA/backlog eligibility rules for now — focus on program, graduation year, 10th/12th percentage which already exist in `StudentDocuments.documentMeta`
> - **Option B**: Add CGPA/backlog fields to the User or StudentProfile model (more work, needs data entry)
>
> **I'm going with Option A unless you say otherwise.**

> [!NOTE]
> **Graduation year** will be derived from `User.courseEndDate`. **10th/12th percentage** will be pulled from `StudentDocuments.documentMeta`.

