## APIs (6 routes)

| # | Route | Method | Auth | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `/api/admin/jobs` | GET, POST | admin | List all jobs, create job |
| 2 | `/api/admin/jobs/[id]` | PATCH, DELETE | admin | Edit/close/delete job |
| 3 | `/api/admin/jobs/[id]/applications` | GET, PATCH | admin | View & update application statuses |
| 4 | `/api/admin/jobs/[id]/referrals` | GET, PATCH | admin | View & update referral statuses |
| 5 | `/api/student/jobs` | GET | student | List published jobs + eligibility check |
| 6 | `/api/student/jobs/[id]/apply` | POST | student | Apply (resume upload) |
| 7 | `/api/student/jobs/[id]/refer` | POST | student | Refer candidate (if enabled) |

---

## Eligibility Engine (pure function)

```
checkEligibility(job, student, docMeta) → { eligible: boolean, reasons: string[] }
```

Checks:
1. ✅ Student profile complete + status active
2. ✅ Job not closed / past deadline
3. ✅ Program in `eligibility.programs` (or all programs allowed)
4. ✅ Graduation year in `eligibility.graduationYears` (derived from `courseEndDate`)
5. ✅ 10th percentage ≥ `min10thPct` (from `documentMeta`)
6. ✅ 12th percentage ≥ `min12thPct` (from `documentMeta`)

