## UI Pages (3 pages)

### Admin: `/admin/jobs` — Job Management
- Table of all jobs (title, company, status, deadline, application count)
- Create/Edit job modal (all fields + eligibility rules + referral config)
- Click into a job → tabbed view: Applications / Referrals
- Status update dropdowns, admin notes

### Student: `/student/jobs` — Job Board
- Cards layout with eligibility badge (✅ / ❌ with reasons)
- Apply button (disabled if not eligible or already applied)
- Refer button (if referral enabled)
- My Applications tab

### No standalone pages needed for:
- Referral form — modal inside the job card
- Application detail — inline in admin table

