## Edge Cases Handled

- ❌ Block apply/refer if `isProfileComplete === false`
- ❌ Block if job `status !== 'published'` or past `deadline`
- ❌ Block self-referral (same email)
- ❌ Duplicate candidateEmail per job
- ✅ Eligibility changes after apply do NOT retroactively invalidate
- ⚠️ Referral + direct application conflict flagged in admin view
